<h4 id="一键卸载命令："><a href="#一键卸载命令：" class="headerlink" title="一键卸载命令："></a>一键卸载命令：</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">卸载 caddy</span><br><span class="line">bash c.sh -unc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">卸载 php+sqlite</span><br><span class="line">bash c.sh -unp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">卸载 v2ray</span><br><span class="line">bash c.sh -unv</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">卸载 rinetdbbr</span><br><span class="line">bash c.sh -unb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

